summary: Ok so I realized something about pepper*ny that has been really bugging me since I first noticed it: Has Pepper actually done...
body:
Ok so I realized something about pepper*ny that has been really bugging me since I first noticed it: Has Pepper actually done anything nice for Tony or even just said something nice about him? I’m genuinely asking. Literally the only thing I can think of is the “Proof Tony Stark has a heart” gift in IM1.

Tony is constantly gushing about her, complimenting her and bringing up how important she is to him.

he made her CEO, used the iron man suit to give her a massage when she came home from work, gotten her gifts and, just to make her happy, he destroyed the suits (something that means the world to him)

Now sure there’s a hug or her calling him “honey” or something now and then but a large chunk of the time she’s just irritated with him & goes on about how frustrating being with him is

summary: Después de habernos presentado a todos los héroes por separado, Marvel studios se atrevió por primera vez a juntara todos sus...
body:
The avengers

Después de habernos presentado a todos los héroes por separado, Marvel studios se atrevió por primera vez a juntara todos sus personajes principales en una gran película, un súper crossover como sucedió en los 60s en los cómics, Los Avengers.

El éxito de esta pelicula fue inmediato, basada en 2 historias de los cómics anteriormente mencionadas en este blog.

Simplemente perfecta y lo mejor de todo es que nos presenta al malvado principal no solo de la película sino de toda esta saga, que culminaría 7 años después.

Muy recomendable.

5 de 5

summary:
This is my first tumblr post, I’ve never used this platform so I don’t know really know how to “present” a post
Anyway I know...
body:
This is my first tumblr post, I’ve never used this platform so I don’t know really know how to “present” a post

Anyway I know it’s very late since the film came out over a year ago but this is my completed Infinity War work, made up of my personal favourite characters who appeared in the film, albeit some very briefly. It was initially intended as a poster but it’s took so long and after Endgame it’s become more of a tribute.

This is without a doubt the most time consuming and ambitious piece of art I’ve ever tried and actually finished. I hope to do more pieces like this in the future and am looking into selling prints of this if people are interested.

sophieannjoyceduffy@gmail.com

Tony: Oh, come on. I mean, am I attracted to Nat? Sure. Do my days feel better when I’m around her? Yeah. Does she get me in ways no man or woman ever has? Indubitably. Do I fantasize about a life we could have together? Constantly. But do I like her? The answer is no.

Rhodey, 100% done: L I S T E N T O Y O U R S E L F
